
graph TD
    %% Start
    A[Start: User Interacts with API] --> B{Choose Action}

    %% User Registration
    B --> |Register| C[POST /api/auth/register/]
    C --> D{Validate registration_number}
    D --> |Exists in CollegeData?| E{Is_used=False?}
    E --> |Yes| F{Course exists?}
    F --> |Yes| G[Return UserSerializer data<br>registration_number, first_name, last_name<br>email, is_verified=False, role='voter'<br>course=Course.name]
    F --> |No| H[Return 400: No course]
    E --> |No| I[Return 400: Data used]
    D --> |No| J[Return 404: Not found]

    %% Registration Completion
    B --> |Complete Registration| K[POST /api/auth/complete-registration/]
    K --> L{Validate data<br>registration_number, email, password<br>state, course_id}
    L --> |Valid| M{Check CollegeData<br>is_used=False?}
    M --> |Yes| N[Create User<br>Set password, is_verified=True<br>Update CollegeData.is_used=True]
    N --> O[Celery Task: Send Welcome Email<br>Via Redis Queue]
    N --> P[Return 200: User created]
    M --> |No| Q[Return 400: Data used]
    L --> |Invalid| R[Return 400: Validation errors]

    %% Login
    B --> |Login| S[POST /api/auth/login/]
    S --> T{Authenticate<br>registration_number, password}
    T --> |Success| U[Generate JWT<br>access, refresh tokens]
    U --> V[Return 200: Tokens]
    T --> |Failure| W[Return 401: Invalid credentials]

    %% Contact Election Commissioner
    B --> |Contact Commissioner| X[POST /api/contact-commissioner/]
    X --> Y{Validate message data<br>sender, message}
    Y --> |Valid| Z[Celery Task: Send Email to Commissioner<br>Via Redis Queue]
    Z --> AA[Return 200: Message sent]
    Y --> |Invalid| AB[Return 400: Validation errors]

    %% Forgotten Password
    B --> |Forgot Password| AC[POST /api/auth/forgot-password/]
    AC --> AD{Validate data<br>registration_number, email<br>state, course}
    AD --> |Valid| AE{User exists?}
    AE --> |Yes| AF[Celery Task: Send Password Reset Email<br>Generate reset token<br>Via Redis Queue]
    AF --> AG[Return 200: Reset email sent]
    AE --> |No| AH[Return 404: User not found]
    AD --> |Invalid| AI[Return 400: Validation errors]

    %% Celery and Redis
    O --> |Async| AJ[Celery Worker: Process Email Task<br>Redis: Queue Task]
    Z --> |Async| AJ
    AF --> |Async| AJ
    AJ --> AK[Email Service: Send Email]
    AJ --> |Blockchain Tasks| AL[Celery Worker: Process Vote<br>Record on Blockchain<br>Redis: Store Task Result]

    %% End
    G --> AM[End]
    P --> AM
    V --> AM
    AA --> AM
    AG --> AM
    H --> AM
    I --> AM
    J --> AM
    Q --> AM
    R --> AM
    W --> AM
    AB --> AM
    AH --> AM
    AI --> AM

